Big Brother Naija 2019, BBNaija, housemate, Ike, on Sunday emerged winner of this week’s ‘Veto Power Game of Chance.’ Housemates were instructed to pick different angle cards and guess the ninja’s angle. The housemate that picked the correct card wins the ‘Veto Power Card.’ After four rounds, Ike won the challenge. Big Brother also said the winner of the game gets the ability to save and replace a nominated housemate even if they were the ones that had been nominated. The winner also received 100 Bet9ja coins. Meanwhile, Gedoni and Jackie were evicted during the live eviction show on Sunday. Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.